ents in England]]\n[[Category:1614 disestablishments]]\n[[Category:1614 in politics]]\n[[Category:Parliaments of James I of England]]\n", "name_user": "Tenpop421", "label": "safe", "comment": "it has been known to posterity as the '''Addled Parliament''' for this legislative failure. \u2192 for this legislative failure it has been known to posterity as the '''Addled Parliament'''.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Addled_Parliament"}
{"title_page": "Jean-Claude Garde", "text_new": "{{short description|French cyclist}}\n{{use dmy dates|date=April 2015}}\n{{Infobox cyclist\n| name           = Jean-Claude Garde\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1960|9|12|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Condrieu]], [[France]]\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| discipline     = \n| role           = Rider\n| ridertype      = \n| amateuryears1  = \n| amateurteam1   = \n| proyears1      = \n| proteam1       = \n| majorwins      = \n| medaltemplates = \n| show-medals    = \n| updated        = \n}}\n'''Jean-Claude Garde''' (born 12 September 1960) is a French former professional [[cycle sport|racing cyclist]].<ref name=\"bio\">{{cite web |url=http://www.procyclingstats.com/rider/Jean_claude_Garde |title=Jean-Claude Garde |accessdate=3 April 2015 |work=Pro Cycling Stats}}</ref> He rode in the [[1986 Tour de France]] and the [[1985 Vuelta a Espa\u00f1a]].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{cycling archives|2937}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Garde, Jean-Claude}}\n[[Category:1960 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Condrieu]]\n[[Category:French male cyclists]]\n[[Category:Tour de France cyclists]]\n[[Category:Vuelta a Espa\u00f1a cyclists]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Rh\u00f4ne (department)]]\n\n\n{{France-cycling-bio-1960s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{use dmy dates|date=April 2015}}\n{{Infobox cyclist\n| name           = Jean-Claude Garde\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1960|9|12|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Condrieu]], [[France]]\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| discipline     = \n| role           = Rider\n| ridertype      = \n| amateuryears1  = \n| amateurteam1   = \n| proyears1      = \n| proteam1       = \n| majorwin